00:39:02,000 --> 00:39:04,000
 Lead us, Lord.

691
00:39:04,000 --> 00:39:07,000
 Lead us.

692
00:39:07,000 --> 00:39:11,000
 May you hear the Holy Spirit say to you today, "Follow me."

